<i> This is Mike Stapleton,
 he's in Ohio.</i>

00:20:38.970 --> 00:20:40.805
<i> He has six, five, six tigers.</i>

00:20:40.805 --> 00:20:42.707
<i> And he is suing the state</i>

00:20:42.707 --> 00:20:44.308
