<i> And you're not going
 to be allowed to have
 one of these animals</i>

00:20:48.613 --> 00:20:51.849
<i> without huge bonds. So,
 these are all rescued animals.</i>

00:20:51.849 --> 00:20:55.420
<i> These were probably photo
 tigers, when they were cubs.</i>

00:20:55.420 --> 00:20:56.654
<i> People had their
 picture made with them.</i>

00:20:56.654 --> 00:20:57.922
<i> Then they get too big.</i>

00:20:58.022 --> 00:21:02.027
